videos.description: Kilton Anderson hooks up with Ky'Jon Tyler for a 28-yard, back-shoulder pass to put Coastal Carolina in the red zone.
videos.headline: Coastal Carolina gets into red zone with 28-yard pass

videos.description: Osharmar Abercrombie runs up the gut for a 1-yard touchdown to give Coastal Carolina a 14-3 lead early in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Abercrombie runs up the middle for TD

videos.description: Kilton Anderson throws a deep ball to Malcolm Williams, who beats his defender down the field for a 67-yard touchdown on the first drive of the game.
videos.headline: Coastal Carolina's Anderson airs out 67-yard TD

videos.description: L.A. Ramsby takes a late pitch and runs down field for a 28-yard gain to Coastal Carolina's 41-yard line.
videos.headline: Ramsby's long run puts Georgia Southern into Coastal Carolina territory

videos.description: Myles Campbell shakes a few tackles and springs to the outside for a 47-yard kickoff return.
videos.headline: Georgia Southern's Campbell opens second half with 47-yard return

videos.description: Shai Werts floats a pass to Ellis Richardson for an 8-yard touchdown and the lead over Coastal Carolina in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Richardson's TD catch gives Georgia Southern the lead

videos.description: Kilton Anderson fakes the handoff, then throws a 37-yard strike to Malcolm Williams for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams puts Coastal Carolina back on top with 37-yard TD

videos.description: Osharmar Abercrombie breaks a tackle and stiff arms another defender for a 41-yard run to the red zone.
videos.headline: Coastal Carolina's Abercrombie shakes tackles for 41-yard run

videos.description: Osharmar Abercrombie finds a little daylight for a 1-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Abercrombie finishes off drive with TD run for Coastal Carolina
